\bmhead{Code availability}

The code for generating the SED is publicly available at \url{http://www.hyperion-rt.org/}. Stable version 1.4 was used to generate the SED. The evolutionary tracks {PARSEC} can be found at \url{http://stev.oapd.inaf.it/cgi-bin/cmd} (version 3.7). The radial fit was performed with Exo-Stricker, version 0.88, and can be found at \url{https://exo-restart.com/tools/the-exo-striker-tool/}. The emcee package is a pure PYTHON package and can be downloaded from \url{https://emcee.readthedocs.io/en/stable/}. The ESO pipeline can be downloaded from \url{https://www.eso.org/sci/software/pipelines/}.

